"title": "5578: tents",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5578: tents",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A portable structure made of cloth or skins used mainly by nomads or semi-nomads. God's tent or tabernacle is a meeting-place with him.</p>\n<h2>Tents as portable dwellings used especially by semi-nomadic peoples</h2>\n<h3>They were living quarters for God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:20\">GEN 4:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:8\">GEN 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:12\">GEN 13:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1\">GEN 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:27\">GEN 25:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:10\">NUM 11:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:10\">1SA 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:1\">2SA 20:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:16\">1KI 12:16</a></p>\n<h3>Sometimes women of distinction had their own tents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:67\">GEN 24:67</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:33\">GEN 31:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:17-Judg4:18\">JDG 4:17–4:18</a></p>\n<h3>A tent housed the ark of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:17\">2SA 6:17</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:1\">1CH 16:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:2\">2SA 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:1\">1CH 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:4\">2CH 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Tents associated with other peoples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:5\">JDG 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:27\">GEN 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:7\">HAB 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Kings and armies camped in tents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:10\">NUM 31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:7-2Kgs7:8\">2KI 7:7–7:8</a></p>\n<h2>Tents for storage</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:54\">1SA 17:54</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21-Josh7:23\">JOS 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h2>Tents were illustrative of a nomadic life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:7\">JER 35:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:9-Heb11:10\">HEB 11:9–11:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:8\">GEN 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:5\">GEN 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:18\">GEN 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1-Gen18:6\">GEN 18:1–18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:13\">GEN 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:16\">EXO 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:8\">EXO 33:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:10\">EXO 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:50\">NUM 1:50</a></p>\n<h2>Tents sometimes associated with sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:22\">JOB 8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:21\">GEN 9:21</a> <em>Noah's drunkenness</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:26\">NUM 16:26</a> <em>the rebellion of Korah, Dathan and Abiram</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:21-Josh7:23\">JOS 7:21–7:23</a> <em>Achan's sin</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:16\">1KI 20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:21\">JOB 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:14\">JOB 11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:6\">JOB 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:34\">JOB 15:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:6\">JOB 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:28\">JOB 21:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:23\">JOB 22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:10\">PSA 84:10</a></p>\n<h2>The construction of tents</h2>\n<h3>Tentmakers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:3\">ACT 18:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The materials used</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:7\">EXO 26:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:14\">EXO 36:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:14-Exod26:29\">EXO 26:14–26:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:19-Exod36:34\">EXO 36:19–36:34</a></p>\n<h3>Tent pegs and ropes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:19\">EXO 27:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:18\">EXO 35:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:20\">EXO 38:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:31\">EXO 38:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:40\">EXO 39:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:26\">NUM 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:37\">NUM 3:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:32\">NUM 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:21\">JDG 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:25\">ISA 22:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:4\">ZEC 10:4</a></p>\n<h3>Colours of tents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:5\">SNG 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:14\">EXO 26:14</a></p>\n<h3>Pitching tents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:20\">JER 10:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:25\">GEN 26:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:19\">GEN 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:11\">JDG 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:22\">2SA 16:22</a></p>\n<h2>The metaphorical use of tents</h2>\n<h3>As an image of creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:2\">PSA 104:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:4\">PSA 19:4</a></p>\n<h3>As a metaphor for death</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1\">2CO 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:13-2Pet1:14\">2PE 1:13–1:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's tent is a meeting-place with him</h2>\n<h3>The tabernacle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:8-Exod25:9\">EXO 25:8–25:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1-Exod26:37\">EXO 26:1–26:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:32\">EXO 39:32</a></p>\n<h3>The Tent of Meeting</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:21\">EXO 27:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:7\">EXO 33:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:43\">EXO 28:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:10-Exod29:11\">EXO 29:10–29:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:30\">EXO 29:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:44\">EXO 29:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:11\">EXO 33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:1\">LEV 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:1\">NUM 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:14-Deut31:15\">DEU 31:14–31:15</a></p>\n<h2>God ``tenting'' with his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:8\">EXO 25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:45-Exod29:46\">EXO 29:45–29:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:38\">EXO 40:34–40:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:11-Lev26:12\">LEV 26:11–26:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:3\">NUM 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:11\">DEU 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:27\">EZK 37:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></p>",
